Module  : Online Users
Version : 2.5.2
Authors : Chris Eaton <tridus@hiredgoons.ca> (original 5.1 module)
          Phorum user Sunbringer (initial 5.1 to 5.2 port)
          Maurice Makaay <maurice@phorum.org> (5.2 rewrite)
          Thomas Seifert <thomas@phorum.org> (database support)

This module shows which users have been seen online recently.
Additionally, it can keep track of the number of guests, visitor
records and the number of active readers for each forum.


Original lincense by Chris:
---------------------------

You are free to use, modify, or redistribute this code as long as I (Chris
Eaton) am given credit for the original development somewhere. This code
comes with absolutly no warranty. It would be nice (but not required) of
you to email me if you find this module useful. :-)


Install:
--------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "onlineusers" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Online Users";

- After this, go to the module's settings screen to configure
  the options for this module.

